name: UFC 200 Greatest Fighters of All Time
original_name: UFC 200 Greatest Fighters of All Time
overview: UFC 200 Greatest Fighters of All Time is a six-part series counting down the best athletes to ever step foot in the UFC Octagon. See the iconic performances and fascinating backstories that elevated champions, contenders and trailblazers into legends of the sport.
